{"tid":2433864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不具名政府人士：新加坡傳媒指民陣違《香港國安法》將被取締屬假新聞","createTime":"2021-03-05T07:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T08:24:37.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"73d0b8cfb436e0a3218c416785a5e79f657a305e","tid":2433864,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:04:55.000Z","msg":"民陣：從未收取任何外國政府或機構資助<br />\n<br />\n有新加坡傳媒引述消息指，香港的民陣由於涉嫌違反《香港國安法》，短時間內可能會被取締。有政府消息人士向本台指，報道並不真確。<br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人陳皓桓則表示，民陣成立至今，從未收取任何外國政府或機構資助，包括美國國家民主基金會，民陣的資金一直是依靠遊行集會期間的市民捐款。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2381709&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUvhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=05b9a8e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381709</a>"},{"pid":"13a3a93ffcd32a9dafefcebd6813995ba8eb853a","tid":2433864,"uid":152476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:07:18.000Z","msg":"點解唔係政府正式回應？<br />\n要搵所謂消息人士？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0cd4b4bec65872a886bbb0002d87861a485fcc","tid":2433864,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:08:49.000Z","msg":"試水溫式警告民陣自行解散 , 過幾個月再拉人告國安法 winwin"},{"pid":"656af9551e1ec75c75e6cd12c29cc28afeab9350","tid":2433864,"uid":275243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:10:17.000Z","msg":"其實個問題係關坡狗乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔係環時新華堆官方喉舌<br />\n又唔係01紅早cctvb用黎放風<br />\n消息靈通又唔係路透級數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed334e0beea4e603bbe18766f2f5b6294cc5826","tid":2433864,"uid":258903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:10:31.000Z","msg":"試口風~~~<br />\n不過而家有無真係無乜分別"},{"pid":"8cec64e49